text: Said al-Harumi or Saeed Alkharumi (, , (January 10, 1972August 25, 2021) was an Israeli politician. He was a member of the Knesset for the Joint List (2017-2021) and the United Arab List (2021). Al-Harumi was born in Shaqib al- Salam, Israel. Al-Harumi died on August 25, 2021 of a heart attack in Beersheba, Israel at the age of 49.Ra'am MK Saeed Alharomi dies at 49 ==References== Category:1972 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Deaths from myocardial infarction Category:Israeli politicians
title: Said al-Harumi
